OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FA cloudy day with outbreaks of
OL,6,Frain, some of this could turn heavy
OL,7,Ffor a time. Becoming mainly dry
OL,8,Fthrough the afternoon with some
OL,9,Fbrightness developing.
OL,10,
OL,11,CTonight:FQuite cloudy at first with
OL,12,Fsome rain possible for Orkney.
OL,13,FBecoming sunny then clear for Shetland
OL,14,Fovernight, cloudier but with some
OL,15,Fclear spells possible for Orkney,
OL,16,Fchance of some showers.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
