OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CSaturday:FA chance of rain for Orkney
OL,6,Fearly on. Otherwise dry with good
OL,7,Fsunny spells for Shetland, quite
OL,8,Fcloudy for Orkney but some bright or
OL,9,Fsunny spells breaking out at times.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FA dry
OL,12,Ffew days with plenty of sunshine on
OL,13,FSunday and Monday, likely turning
OL,14,Fsomewhat cloudier on Tuesday but still
OL,15,Fsome sunny spells. Winds will be light.
